{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"717d3d5c810ce1da","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TB\n    subgraph MainWindow [\"MainWindow (Shell.xaml)\"]\n        direction TB\n        \n        subgraph TopBar [\"顶部工具栏\"]\n            Logo[\"Logo / 返回按钮\"]\n            Menu[\"主菜单\\nCollection / Settings / Info\"]\n            SysCtrl[\"系统设置 / 窗口控制\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph ThreePane [\"三栏主内容区\"]\n            direction LR\n            LeftPane[\"左栏\\nPrimaryFilter\\n(艺术家/专辑/流派)\"]\n            MiddlePane[\"中栏\\nMainContent\\n(曲目列表)\"]\n            RightPane[\"右栏\\nExtension\\n(歌词/信息)\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph BottomBar [\"底部状态栏\"]\n            Spectrum[\"频谱分析器\"]\n            PlayCtrl[\"播放控制\\n(上一曲/播放/下一曲)\"]\n            Progress[\"进度条\"]\n        end\n        \n        TopBar --> ThreePane\n        ThreePane --> BottomBar\n    end\n    \n    style TopBar fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3,stroke-width:2px\n    style ThreePane fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px\n    style BottomBar fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:2px\n```","x":-560,"y":-689,"width":520,"height":1380},
		{"id":"82bac8dd951aba03","type":"text","text":"| 层级          | 技术                     | 用途           |\n| :---------- | :--------------------- | :----------- |\n| **UI 框架**   | WPF + XAML             | 界面渲染         |\n| **MVVM 框架** | Prism                  | 依赖注入、导航、事件   |\n| **音频引擎**    | CSCore                 | 音频解码与播放      |\n| **音频解码**    | FFmpeg (CSCore.Ffmpeg) | 多格式支持        |\n| **音频输出**    | WASAPI / DirectSound   | Windows 音频输出 |\n| **数据库**     | SQLite                 | 数据持久化        |\n| **ORM**     | SQLite-net-pcl         | 数据库操作        |\n| **序列化**     | Newtonsoft.Json        | JSON 处理      |\n| **外部集成**    | DiscordRPC             | Discord 状态   |","x":-560,"y":691,"width":560,"height":369},
		{"id":"561f130152c02480","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph BT\n    Tests[\"Dopamine.Tests\"]\n    \n    subgraph Main [\"Dopamine (主程序)\"]\n        UI[\"Views + ViewModels\"]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Services [\"Dopamine.Services\"]\n        Srv[\"所有服务实现\"]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Core [\"Dopamine.Core\"]\n        Audio[\"音频引擎\"]\n        API[\"外部API\"]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Data [\"Dopamine.Data\"]\n        Repo[\"Repositories\"]\n        DB[(\"SQLite\")]\n    end\n    \n    Tests -.-> Main\n    Tests -.-> Services\n    Tests -.-> Core\n    \n    Main --> Services\n    Services --> Core\n    Services --> Data\n    Core --> Data\n    \n    style Main fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3,stroke-width:2px\n    style Services fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px\n    style Core fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:2px\n    style Data fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292,stroke-width:2px\n    style Tests fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#9c27b0,stroke-dasharray: 5 5\n```","x":2720,"y":-689,"width":632,"height":820},
		{"id":"3bef42d997d641b5","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    %% 展示层：WPF UI\n    subgraph UI_Layer [\"🎨 Presentation Layer (WPF + Prism)\"]\n        direction TB\n        \n        subgraph Shell [\"Shell (Main Window)\"]\n            direction LR\n            TopBar[\"顶部工具栏\\nLogo / 菜单 / 窗口控制\"]\n            MainContent[\"主内容区\\n(三栏布局)\"]\n            BottomBar[\"底部状态栏\\n频谱 / 播放控制\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph Views [\"Views (XAML)\"]\n            FV[\"FullPlayerView\\n完整播放器\"]\n            MV[\"MiniPlayerView\\n迷你播放器\"]\n            NP[\"NowPlayingView\\n正在播放\"]\n            CV[\"CollectionViews\\n收藏/设置/信息\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph ViewModels [\"ViewModels\"]\n            MainVM[\"MainViewModel\"]\n            PlayerVM[\"PlayerViewModel\"]\n            CollectionVM[\"CollectionViewModels\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    %% 服务层\n    subgraph Service_Layer [\"⚙️ Service Layer (Dopamine.Services)\"]\n        direction LR\n        PS[\"IPlaybackService\\n播放控制\"]\n        NS[\"INotificationService\\n系统通知\"]\n        MS[\"IMetadataService\\n元数据\"]\n        IS[\"IIndexingService\\n音乐索引\"]\n        ES[\"IEqualizerService\\n均衡器\"]\n        CS[\"ICollectionService\\n收藏管理\"]\n        SS[\"ISearchService\\n搜索\"]\n        DS[\"IDiscordService\\nDiscord\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 核心层\n    subgraph Core_Layer [\"🛡️ Core Layer (Dopamine.Core)\"]\n        direction TB\n        \n        subgraph Audio [\"Audio Engine\"]\n            CSP[\"CSCorePlayer\\n核心播放器\"]\n            EQ[\"EqualizerPreset\\n均衡器预设\"]\n            SP[\"ISpectrumPlayer\\n频谱分析\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph Api [\"External APIs\"]\n            LFM[\"LastFm API\"]\n            LYR[\"Lyrics API\"]\n            FAN[\"Fanart API\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph IO [\"IO & Utils\"]\n            PLD[\"PlaylistDecoder\\n播放列表\"]\n            FU[\"FormatUtils\\n格式化\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    %% 数据层\n    subgraph Data_Layer [\"💾 Data Layer (Dopamine.Data)\"]\n        direction TB\n        SQLite[(\"SQLite Database\")]\n        TR[\"TrackRepository\"]\n        FR[\"FolderRepository\"]\n        PR[\"PlaylistRepository\"]\n        Entities[\"Entities\\nTrack / Folder / Blacklist\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 依赖注入容器\n    DI((\"Prism DI\\nContainer\"))\n\n    %% 连接关系\n    UI_Layer -- \"依赖注入\" --> DI\n    DI -- \"解析服务\" --> Service_Layer\n    Service_Layer -- \"调用\" --> Core_Layer\n    Service_Layer -- \"持久化\" --> Data_Layer\n    \n    %% 视觉美化\n    style UI_Layer fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3,stroke-width:2px\n    style Service_Layer fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px\n    style Core_Layer fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:2px\n    style Data_Layer fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292,stroke-width:2px\n    style DI fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#9c27b0,stroke-dasharray: 5 5\n```\n","x":0,"y":-689,"width":2685,"height":2480},
		{"id":"cfbb48fd41c83d85","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TB\n    subgraph Container [\"Prism DI Container\"]\n        direction LR\n        \n        subgraph CoreServices [\"核心服务\"]\n            PS[\"IPlaybackService\\n→ PlaybackService\"]\n            MS[\"IMetadataService\\n→ MetadataService\"]\n            IS[\"IIndexingService\\n→ IndexingService\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph UIServices [\"UI 相关服务\"]\n            NS[\"INotificationService\\n→ NotificationService\"]\n            TS[\"ITaskbarService\\n→ TaskbarService\"]\n            AS[\"IAppearanceService\\n→ AppearanceService\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph ExternalServices [\"外部集成\"]\n            DS[\"IDiscordService\\n→ DiscordService\"]\n            UPS[\"IUpdateService\\n→ UpdateService\"]\n            LFS[\"ILastFmService\\n→ LastFmService\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph DataServices [\"数据服务\"]\n            CS[\"ICollectionService\\n→ CollectionService\"]\n            SS[\"ISearchService\\n→ SearchService\"]\n            PLS[\"IPlaylistService\\n→ PlaylistService\"]\n        end\n    end\n    \n    style CoreServices fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3\n    style UIServices fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800\n    style ExternalServices fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50\n    style DataServices fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292\n```","x":2685,"y":221,"width":1080,"height":940},
		{"id":"7fefbe82fc6d8b93","type":"text","text":"","x":1888,"y":2260,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"308d45d267b5ce41","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    User((\"用户\"))\n    \n    subgraph UI [\"UI Layer\"]\n        PC[\"播放按钮\\nPlayCommand\"]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Service [\"Service Layer\"]\n        PB[\"IPlaybackService\\nPlay()\"]\n        QM[\"QueueManager\\n队列管理\"]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Core [\"Core Layer\"]\n        CSP[\"CSCorePlayer\\n播放引擎\"]\n        FF[\"FFmpeg\\n解码器\"]\n        WAS[\"WASAPI\\n音频输出\"]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Feedback [\"反馈通知\"]\n        NS[\"NotificationService\\nToast通知\"]\n        DS[\"DiscordService\\n状态同步\"]\n        TB[\"TaskbarService\\n任务栏进度\"]\n    end\n    \n    User -- \"点击\" --> PC\n    PC -- \"调用\" --> PB\n    PB -- \"管理\" --> QM\n    PB -- \"驱动\" --> CSP\n    CSP -- \"解码\" --> FF\n    CSP -- \"输出\" --> WAS\n    \n    PB -. \"事件通知\" .-> NS\n    PB -. \"状态同步\" .-> DS\n    PB -. \"进度更新\" .-> TB\n    \n    style UI fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3\n    style Service fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800\n    style Core fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50\n    style Feedback fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#9c27b0\n```","x":120,"y":1800,"width":1580,"height":980},
		{"id":"a5b2909f40380210","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\nerDiagram\n    TRACK ||--o{ METADATA : has\n    TRACK {\n        int TrackId PK\n        string Path\n        string Title\n        string Artist\n        string Album\n        int Duration\n    }\n    \n    FOLDER ||--o{ TRACK : contains\n    FOLDER {\n        int FolderId PK\n        string Path\n        string Name\n    }\n    \n    PLAYLIST ||--o{ TRACK : includes\n    PLAYLIST {\n        int PlaylistId PK\n        string Name\n        string Type\n    }\n    \n    BLACKLIST_TRACK {\n        int BlacklistTrackId PK\n        string Path\n    }\n    \n    METADATA {\n        int MetadataId PK\n        int TrackId FK\n        string Key\n        string Value\n    }\n```","x":1700,"y":1800,"width":653,"height":637},
		{"id":"b039fe3e2d2740a5","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    %% 展示层：采用层级嵌套\n    subgraph UI_Layer [\"🎨 Presentation Layer (WPF + Prism)\"]\n        direction TB\n        subgraph Shell [\"MainWindow (Universal Shell)\"]\n            R1[\"PrimaryFilterRegion (Sidebar)\"]\n            R2[\"MainContentRegion (View Stack)\"]\n            R3[\"ControlRegion (Player Bar)\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph Views [\"Functional Views\"]\n            SBV[\"SideBarView (Category/Playlist)\"]\n            LVV[\"LibraryView (Dopamine Flow)\"]\n            PCV[\"PlaybackBarView (Iconic Control)\"]\n            \n            subgraph DV [\"DetailView (Deep Workspace)\"]\n                LT[\"LeftTop (Lyrics/MiniList Switch)\"]\n                LB[\"LeftBottom (AlbumCover)\"]\n                RW[\"RightPanel (LoopWorkspace Area)\"]\n            end\n        end\n        \n        R1 --> SBV\n        R2 -- \"Nav: Library\" --> LVV\n        R2 -- \"Nav: Detail\" --> DV\n        R3 --> PCV\n    end\n\n    %% 服务层：逻辑中枢\n    subgraph Service_Layer [\"⚙️ Service & Logic Layer (DI Singleton)\"]\n        direction LR\n        PS[\"IPlayerService (Audio Logic)\"]\n        PMS[\"IPlaylistManager (Collection)\"]\n        LAS[\"ILoopAnalysis (DSP Manager)\"]\n        LS[\"ILocalization (i18n Engine)\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 核心层：基础设施\n    subgraph Infrastructure [\"🛡️ Infrastructure & Asset Core\"]\n        direction TB\n        AL[\"AudioLooper (State Machine)\"]\n        Str[\"LoopStream (Seamless Engine)\"]\n        DB[\"Database (SQLite / Dapper)\"]\n        PyW[\"PyMusicLooper (AI Wrapper)\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 通讯机制\n    Bus((\"Prism EventAggregator\"))\n\n    %% 数据与指令流\n    UI_Layer -- \"Resolved Commands\" --> Service_Layer\n    Service_Layer -- \"Drive\" --> AL\n    AL -- \"Feed\" --> Str\n    Service_Layer -- \"Persistence\" --> DB\n    LAS -- \"Analyze\" --> PyW\n    \n    %% 消息传递\n    Service_Layer -. \"Broadcast Events\" .-> Bus\n    Bus -. \"Update UI\" .-> UI_Layer\n\n    %% 视觉美化方案\n    style UI_Layer fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292,stroke-width:2px\n    style Service_Layer fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3,stroke-width:2px\n    style Infrastructure fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:2px\n    style Bus fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-dasharray: 5 5\n```","x":1343,"y":-2600,"width":2064,"height":1491},
		{"id":"4e5cc05d2320f3ef","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    %% 展示层：采用层级嵌套\n    subgraph UI_Layer [\"🎨 Presentation Layer (WPF + Prism)\"]\n        direction TB\n        subgraph Shell [\"MainWindow (Universal Shell)\"]\n            R1[\"PrimaryFilterRegion (Sidebar)\"]\n            R2[\"MainContentRegion (View Stack)\"]\n            R3[\"ControlRegion (Player Bar)\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph Views [\"Functional Views\"]\n            SBV[\"SideBarView (Category/Playlist)\"]\n            LVV[\"LibraryView (Dopamine Flow)\"]\n            PCV[\"PlaybackBarView (Iconic Control)\"]\n            \n            subgraph DV [\"DetailView (Deep Workspace)\"]\n                LT[\"LeftTop (Lyrics/MiniList Switch)\"]\n                LB[\"LeftBottom (AlbumCover)\"]\n                RW[\"RightPanel (LoopWorkspace Area)\"]\n            end\n        end\n        \n        subgraph Ext [\"System UI (Polish)\"]\n            NV[\"ToastNotification (Modern)\"]\n            MV[\"MiniPlayer (Acrylic)\"]\n        end\n        \n        R1 --> SBV\n        R2 -- \"Nav: Library\" --> LVV\n        R2 -- \"Nav: Detail\" --> DV\n        R3 --> PCV\n    end\n\n    %% 服务层：逻辑中枢\n    subgraph Service_Layer [\"⚙️ Service & Logic Layer (DI Singleton)\"]\n        direction LR\n        PS[\"IPlayerService (Audio Logic)\"]\n        PMS[\"IPlaylistManager (Collection)\"]\n        \n        subgraph SysSrv [\"System Integrations\"]\n            ITS[\"ITaskbarService (Overlay)\"]\n            INS[\"INotificationService (Toasts)\"]\n            IDS[\"IDiscordService (RPC)\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph MetaSrv [\"Information Retrieval\"]\n            IMS[\"IMetadataService (Tags)\"]\n            ILS[\"ILyricsService (API)\"]\n        end\n        \n        LAS[\"ILoopAnalysis (DSP Manager)\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 核心层：基础设施\n    subgraph Infrastructure [\"🛡️ Infrastructure & Asset Core\"]\n        direction TB\n        AL[\"AudioLooper (State Machine)\"]\n        Str[\"LoopStream (Seamless Engine)\"]\n        \n        subgraph Data [\"Data Persistence\"]\n            RP[\"Repository Pattern (Isolation)\"]\n            DB[\"Database (SQLite / Dapper)\"]\n        end\n        \n        PyW[\"PyMusicLooper (AI Wrapper)\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 通讯机制\n    Bus((\"Prism EventAggregator\"))\n\n    %% 数据与指令流\n    UI_Layer -- \"Commands\" --> Service_Layer\n    Service_Layer -- \"Drive\" --> AL\n    AL -- \"Feed\" --> Str\n    \n    Service_Layer -- \"Query\" --> RP\n    RP -- \"Persistence\" --> DB\n    \n    LAS -- \"Analyze\" --> PyW\n    \n    %% 消息传递\n    Service_Layer -. \"Events\" .-> Bus\n    Bus -. \"Update UI\" .-> UI_Layer\n\n    %% 视觉美化方案\n    style UI_Layer fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292,stroke-width:2px\n    style Service_Layer fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3,stroke-width:2px\n    style Infrastructure fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:2px\n    style Bus fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-dasharray: 5 5\n```","x":580,"y":-5020,"width":3840,"height":1520},
		{"id":"0b829cd1c3618d1b","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    %% 展示层：二栏全局骨架\n    subgraph UI_Layer [\"🎨 Presentation Layer (WPF + Prism)\"]\n        direction TB\n        subgraph Shell [\"MainWindow (Global Skeleton)\"]\n            direction LR\n            Sidebar[\"SidebarRegion (左侧 - 250px)\\n歌单与过滤器层\"]\n            MainRegion[\"MainContentRegion (右侧 - *)\\n动态视图投射层\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph View_States [\"右侧主展区视图形态 (Navigatable Views)\"]\n            direction TB\n            LV[\"LibraryView (一阶段：多巴胺列表)\\n宽敞选曲、封面阵列\"]\n            \n            subgraph DV [\"DetailView (二阶段：深度工作详情)\"]\n                LT[\"左上：歌词 / 迷你曲目列表切换\"]\n                LB[\"左下：Premium 专辑封面\"]\n                RW[\"右侧：LoopWorkspace (操作中枢)\"]\n            end\n        end\n        \n        Sidebar -- \"Trigger Select\" --> LV\n        LV -- \"Trigger Edit/Detail\" --> DV\n        SidebarRegion --> Sidebar\n        MainContentRegion --> MainRegion\n    end\n\n    %% 服务层与核心层\n    subgraph Logic_Core [\"⚙️ logic & Core Services\"]\n        PS[\"IPlayerService\\n播放控制\"]\n        PMS[\"IPlaylistManager\\n歌单中转\"]\n        LAS[\"ILoopAnalysis\\n寻环核心\"]\n        Str[\"LoopStream\\n无缝解码引擎\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 消息机制\n    Bus((\"Prism EventBus\"))\n\n    %% 数据驱动流\n    Sidebar -- \"Publish SelectedPlaylist\" --> Bus\n    Bus -- \"Subscribe & Update\" --> LV\n    LV -- \"Publish EnterEditMode\" --> Bus\n    Bus -- \"Navigate & Switch\" --> DV\n    \n    style UI_Layer fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292,stroke-width:2px\n    style DetailView fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#9c27b0\n    style Logic_Core fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3\n    style Bus fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-dasharray: 5 5\n```","x":3560,"y":-3500,"width":2949,"height":1080},
		{"id":"e10c06d6fc941860","x":4080,"y":-2280,"width":3040,"height":1740,"type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    %% 展示层：二栏全局骨架 + 深度下钻\n    subgraph UI_Layer [\"🎨 Presentation Layer (WPF + Prism)\"]\n        direction TB\n        subgraph Shell [\"MainWindow (Universal Shell)\"]\n            direction LR\n            Sidebar[\"Sidebar (左导航: 250px)\\nCategory / Playlist / Folders\"]\n            MainRegion[\"MainContentRegion (右展示: *)\\nDynamic View Manager\"]\n        end\n        \n        subgraph Views [\"Functional Views & States\"]\n            direction TB\n            LV[\"LibraryView (主库视图)\\n封面列表 / 搜索 / 多选管理\"]\n            \n            subgraph DV [\"DetailView (二阶段：深度工作详情)\"]\n                LT[\"LeftTop: Lyrics/MiniList Switch\"]\n                LB[\"LeftBottom: AlbumCover (Fixed)\"]\n                RW[\"RightPanel: LoopWorkspace (DSP)\"]\n            end\n        end\n        \n        Sidebar -- \"SelectionChange\" --> LV\n        LV -- \"Nav: EditLoop\" --> DV\n        \n        subgraph SystemUI [\"System Integration UI\"]\n            NV[\"ToastNotification\\n(Modern Popups)\"]\n            TV[\"TaskbarOverlay\\n(Progress/Status)\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    %% 服务层：逻辑分治\n    subgraph Service_Layer [\"⚙️ Service Layer (High Cohesion)\"]\n        direction LR\n        PS[\"IPlaybackService\\n播放引擎调度\"]\n        PMS[\"IPlaylistManager\\n曲目集合管理\"]\n        LAS[\"ILoopAnalysis\\nDSP 算法管理\"]\n        \n        subgraph SupportSrv [\"Infrastructure Services\"]\n            ITS[\"ITaskbarService\"]\n            INS[\"INotificationService\"]\n            IDS[\"IDiscordService\"]\n            ILS[\"ILyricsService\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    %% 核心与数据层：极致隔离\n    subgraph Backend_Core [\"🛡️ Architecture Core & Persistence\"]\n        direction TB\n        Core[\"Audio Engine (NAudio Implementation)\\nAudioLooper | LoopStream\"]\n        \n        subgraph Data [\"Data Layer (Isolated)\"]\n            RP[\"Repository Pattern\\nTrackRepository | PlaylistRepository\"]\n            DB[\"Database (SQLite / Dapper)\"]\n        end\n        \n        AI[\"AI Integration\\nPyMusicLooper Wrapper\"]\n    end\n\n    %% 通讯机制\n    EB((\"Prism EventAggregator\\n(Decoupled Messaging Bus)\"))\n\n    %% 交互流向\n    UI_Layer -- \"Resolved Commands\" --> Service_Layer\n    Service_Layer -- \"Drive Control\" --> Core\n    Service_Layer -- \"Query/Save\" --> RP\n    RP -- \"Storage\" --> DB\n    LAS -- \"Process\" --> AI\n    \n    %% 全局通讯\n    Service_Layer -. \"Pub Events\" .-> EB\n    EB -. \"Observe & Sync\" .-> UI_Layer\n\n    %% 视觉美化方案\n    style UI_Layer fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#f06292,stroke-width:2px\n    style DetailView fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#9c27b0\n    style Service_Layer fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#2196f3\n    style Backend_Core fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4caf50\n    style EB fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-dasharray: 5 5\n```"}
	],
	"edges":[]
}